summary: The full moon is rising, don\'t miss it
descriptionHtml:
There was a model that i really liked, but felt it was way too revealing. I made this, just to try it out also to see if anyone else appreciated what i created(Hopefully inspire more)

I am not an artist...and my very first attempt at modding. Thanks to Caliente for bringing us CBBEv2, thanks to Killer Keos for Skimpy Steel mesh that i could play with.  Huge thanks to loyal Xulin for his inspiring Nocturnal Ebony Armor -CBBE version(personally think it\'s a little overboard).

released in .7z .zip .rar formats. There are 6 default named meshes to drag and drop into your Meshes/armor or Meshes/clothes folder. Place FMbikini folder into your textures folder(allows you to rename the mesh to your favorite or most hated outfit).
